ih		 	FLbox  	"'Isorhythm' is a technique whereby a series of durations     ", 	1,      5,     14,    490,    15,     5,  40
ih		 	FLbox  	"forming a rhythm is applied to a row of notes. Normally the  ", 	1,      5,     14,    490,    15,     5,  60
